# OmniAgent

A multi-task intelligent agent framework based on LangChain 1.0.

## Features

- Multi-tool integration (weather, time, knowledge base)
- Conversational interface
- Streamlit web interface
- Knowledge base management

## Installation

```bash
# Create virtual environment
uv venv

# Install dependencies
uv pip install -e .
```

## Usage

### Command line

```bash
uv run python main.py
```

### Web interface

```bash
uv run streamlit run web/app.py
```

## Dependencies

- langchain>=1.0.0
- langchain-openai
- langchain-chroma
- langchain-community
- chromadb
- dashscope
- python-dotenv
- streamlit
- requests
- pypinyin
- langgraph

## Project Structure

- `agent/` - Agent executor and core logic
- `rag/` - Retrieval Augmented Generation (RAG) functionality
- `tools/` - Various tools (weather, time, etc.)
- `config/` - Configuration files
- `prompts/` - Prompt templates
- `knowledge/` - Knowledge base files
- `web/` - Streamlit web interface
- `main.py` - Command line entry point
